        <div style="width: 60%; float: left"><p>Aap Kar Sakte hai Chamatkar (Hindi), available in paperback, is a success guide. It consists of practical approaches one can follow to achieve their goals. The book is written in a language that is easy to follow.</p>
        <p>The book contains many methods based on principles that are inspired from paradigms like ancient wisdom to modern thinking. The issues faced by people on a day-to-day basis are discussed. Solutions for the same are also given which help readers get a clear picture of the values that one must possess to be on the right track.</p>
        <p>In Aap Kar Sakte hai Chamatkar, the author speaks about three categories of people. There are some people who lead their lives driven by inspiration and play just to win. Then there are those who are always desperate to achieve their goals and play not to lose. The last category of people are those who change their positive thoughts into actions, leading to a winning situation.</p>
            <p>Aap Kar Sakte hai Chamatkar (Hindi) is an attempt to help people analyze their own lives and align themselves to their dreams. It lets the readers figure out the kind of force that is driving their lives. The contents of this book mainly concentrate on helping people to translate their positivity into victory. It extensively discusses how the right attitude, self-esteem and interpersonal skills are important to get a winning edge. The book helps the readers to drive their ambitious nature.</p>
            </div>
    </div>
